{"tid":634602,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"明明大家都係好在意對方，但係最後。。","createTime":"2018-04-19T11:26:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-23T01:47:40.000Z","uid":17214,"like":91,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"34411ee64c92f6d716c415af3920432d0e8d6ff1","tid":634602,"uid":17214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T11:26:34.000Z","msg":"唔知咁多位巴絲有冇試過，明明係一段關係入面大家都好在意對方，但有時候岀現左問題，就係因為無人願意出聲，以為咩都在心中對方就會感覺得到或者問題就會自己解決<br />\n到最後，明明一段雙方都好在意嘅關係就咁無聲無息結束左<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n望住以前大家啲合照，原來曾經大家一齊咁開心過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，由曾經嘅摯友，呢家變到相見不相識，個種感覺真係傷心到極點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99bcf43ffcaa7de6526da8607b446597477f4544","tid":634602,"uid":17214,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T11:32:26.000Z","msg":"明明你也曾愛我，沒理由愛不到結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81154362591f7014e59cdc2f630d142d36d3131b","tid":634602,"uid":17214,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T11:33:24.000Z","msg":"只要你敢不懦弱，憑什麼我們要錯過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68b96721ea551aea945204a8046c8abcf0c11102","tid":634602,"uid":59240,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T11:33:46.000Z","msg":"I know that feels<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97cc7b103556f52675752a92fa02961f1007d584","tid":634602,"uid":59240,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T11:34:45.000Z","msg":"兩個都係被動嘅人真係好難行<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d18531fa16bb56bc499cba4c3b1bacaff5606da","tid":634602,"uid":17214,"like":0,"di